edu.uidaho.junicon.interpreter.interpreter

Interface IInterpreterContext

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IInterpreter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractShell, CommandShell, JuniconInterpreter, TransformInterpreter

    public interface IInterpreterContext
    Context for a transformational interpreter, such as parent, dispatch children, and other subordinate classes set by dependency injection.
